    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah, we checked the logs and they mostly look fine. it's not like there are big thefts or anything. it's just these tiny, annoying gaps that dont make sense. like we count them one day they're there, next week a few are just... gone. any ideas on what else could cause that besides just people stealing stuff?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
