      "content": "we looked into the kitting and the scrap logs and they're all pretty much up to date. it feels almost like they're just vanishing into thin air. just tiny amounts, but it's weirdly consistent. do you think it could be something stupidly simple like a unit of measure mix up in the system or just bad luck with the physical audits?",
